Fy_hexic by goombus

Map type: Fight Yard
Number of players: 24

Here is another quick and simple fightyard map with hexagons for cover ^^

This is mainlly for deathmatches, but simple play also works. 
This uses buyzones rather than weapon pick.

Have fun!

Place the bsp. and nav. file into this directory.

C:\Program Files\Steam\steamapps\(username)\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps

(Update! : chizbone's new nav file has been added.)
